保证惊奇,我早料到会这样
Absolutely marvelous...

932
01:12:32,791 --> 01:12:34,416
维多...
Victor...

933
01:12:36,208 --> 01:12:39,458
维多,请给我一点时间
Victor. Victor.

934
01:14:53,833 --> 01:14:55,208
是谁伤害你?
Who hurt you?

935
01:14:55,750 --> 01:14:57,500
我有东西给你看,威廉
I have to show you this, William.

936
01:14:58,500 --> 01:15:00,124
我帮你整理好
Let me organize it for you.

937
01:15:00,125 --> 01:15:02,375
我也有东西给你看
And I have something to show to you.

938
01:15:04,041 --> 01:15:06,000
我跟皇家医学会谈过了
I've spoken to the Royal Medical Society.

939
01:15:06,750 --> 01:15:09,208
- 他们很想见你一面 - 不行,时候未到
- They're interested in seeing you. - No, no, no, not yet.

940
01:15:09,958 --> 01:15:11,208
我还没准备好
I'm not quite ready yet.

941
01:15:12,333 --> 01:15:14,416
我还以为那是你的心愿
I thought that's what you always wanted.

942
01:15:18,416 --> 01:15:19,541
那个人
The man.

943
01:15:20,500 --> 01:15:22,208
- 楼下那个人 - 你看到他了?
- The man downstairs. - You saw him?

944
01:15:22,916 --> 01:15:25,166
他是病人吗?受害者?
Is he a patient? A victim?

945
01:15:27,083 --> 01:15:29,207
他的伤口,你把他打得遍体鳞伤
His wounds. You wounded him like that.

946
01:15:29,208 --> 01:15:31,999
不是我,伊莉莎白 是这个世界伤害他
No, no, no. It was the world that hurt him, Elizabeth.

947
01:15:32,000 --> 01:15:33,833
我...我赋予他生命
I... I gave him life.

948
01:15:35,416 --> 01:15:36,625
我赋予他生命
I gave him life.

949
01:15:39,000 --> 01:15:40,041
起来...
Up, up, up.

950
01:15:40,750 --> 01:15:41,750
来吧
Come on.

951
01:15:44,166 --> 01:15:45,457
这里就好
There, there, there...

952
01:15:45,458 --> 01:15:47,375
他还在适应周遭环境
He's still getting used to his surroundings.

953
01:15:51,125 --> 01:15:53,165
牠很强壮,威廉
It is strong, William.

954
01:15:53,166 --> 01:15:55,125
- 你成功了 - 牠非常强壮
- You did it. - It's so strong.

955
01:15:55,791 --> 01:15:56,750
你真的成功了
You did it.

956
01:15:57,333 --> 01:15:59,290
全身系统都运作正常
All its systems are functional.

957
01:15:59,291 --> 01:16:00,750
伤口都痊愈了
All healing.

958
01:16:01,583 --> 01:16:04,375
这种疗愈能力的确古怪
And the healing is erratic, yes.

959
01:16:05,083 --> 01:16:06,500
但是绝无仅有
But exceptional.

960
01:16:14,583 --> 01:16:16,207
为什么他被锁在这里?
Why is he chained here?

961
01:16:16,208 --> 01:16:17,874
这是为了他和我的安全着想
For his own safety and for mine,

962
01:16:17,875 --> 01:16:21,624
也比较容易清洁和管理
and it's easy to clean and, uh, maintain it.

963
01:16:21,625 --> 01:16:23,125
牠什么都不懂
And it doesn't know any better.

964
01:16:24,500 --> 01:16:25,500
可是你懂
But you do.

965
01:16:28,708 --> 01:16:29,916
哈兰德知情吗?
Does Harlander know?

966
01:16:32,375 --> 01:16:34,999
我们得做好万全准备等他回来...
We have to prepare everything for the moment he returns.

967
01:16:35,000 --> 01:16:37,458
- 那当然 - ...让一切上得了台面
- Of course. - And have everything presentable.

968
01:16:40,750 --> 01:16:42,666
牠有智慧吗?
Is it intelligent?

969
01:16:46,416 --> 01:16:48,166
维多,牠有智慧吗?
Victor, is it intelligent?

970
01:17:02,625 --> 01:17:05,250
我搞不清楚你到底是怎么办到的
I can't fathom how exactly you did what you did,

971
01:17:05,833 --> 01:17:07,750
但我知道这件事意义非凡
but its dimension does not escape me.

972
01:17:10,291 --> 01:17:14,000
维多,你可曾问过自己
Victor, did you ever ask yourself,

973
01:17:15,041 --> 01:17:16,916
组成那个人的所有部分中
of all the parts that make that man,

974
01:17:17,833 --> 01:17:19,916
灵魂位在哪里?
which one holds the soul?

975
01:17:26,458 --> 01:17:27,958
我没问过
No, I didn't.

976
01:17:28,916 --> 01:17:32,375
楼下那怪物叫人惶惶不安
There's something so disquieting about that creature down there.

977
01:17:33,250 --> 01:17:36,541
样貌扭曲,犹如哈哈镜中 有人探头探脑的倒影
Askew, like a figure peeking around a funhouse mirror.

978
01:17:37,208 --> 01:17:38,125
但牠是活物
But animated.

979
01:17:39,250 --> 01:17:40,375
是什么让牠活起来的?
Animated by what?

980
01:18:45,416 --> 01:18:46,416
会不会痛?
Does it hurt?

981
01:18:54,500 --> 01:18:55,458
树叶?
A leaf?

982
01:18:55,958 --> 01:18:56,958
给我的?
For me?

983
01:18:57,833 --> 01:18:58,958
谢谢
Thank you.

984
01:19:03,041 --> 01:19:04,375
好美喔
Isn't it beautiful?

985
01:19:05,875 --> 01:19:06,833
这要送我的吗?
This is for me?

986
01:19:08,500 --> 01:19:09,666
我是伊莉莎白
I'm Elizabeth.

987
01:19:11,625 --> 01:19:13,125
你会说「伊莉莎白」吗?
Can you say "Elizabeth"?

988
01:19:14,291 --> 01:19:15,416
伊莉莎白
Elizabeth.

989
01:19:16,625 --> 01:19:18,875
用喉咙发出声音
My throat makes sounds.

990
01:19:19,750 --> 01:19:20,833
伊莉莎白
Elizabeth.

991
01:19:37,750 --> 01:19:38,916
我要走了
I'm going to go now.

992
01:19:53,625 --> 01:19:56,916
伊莉...莎白
Eliza... beth.

993
01:19:58,833 --> 01:20:00,583
你不应该靠近牠
You should not go near it.

994
01:20:02,666 --> 01:20:03,541
「牠」?
"It"?

995
01:20:05,625 --> 01:20:07,333
牠,没错
It. Yes.

996
01:20:08,166 --> 01:20:12,374
我想牠的体内有生命 但没有智慧的火花
I believe there is life in it,
but not the spark of intelligence that I had intended.

997
01:20:12,375 --> 01:20:13,457
事与愿违

998
01:20:13,458 --> 01:20:15,165
也许不是你所理解的那种
Perhaps not as you understand it.

999
01:20:15,166 --> 01:20:16,874
有地方出了差错
Something went wrong.

1000
01:20:16,875 --> 01:20:19,374
阻塞物、缝合处、连结点
A blockage, a suture, a connection.

1001
01:20:19,375 --> 01:20:21,957
你,伟大的维多弗兰肯斯坦会犯错?
You, the great Victor Frankenstein, you made a mistake?

1002
01:20:21,958 --> 01:20:24,249
怪物只会说一个词,就一个
The Creature knows but one word, and one word alone.

1003
01:20:24,250 --> 01:20:27,165
「维多...」
"Victor, Victor, Victor, Victor."

1004
01:20:27,166 --> 01:20:28,832
毫无韵律或理由地不断重复
It just parrots it without rhyme or reason.

1005
01:20:28,833 --> 01:20:32,082
对他而言,也许那个词暂时代表一切
Perhaps for the time being that word means everything to him.

1006
01:20:32,083 --> 01:20:35,415
或许重生使他复活的灵魂更单纯
What if in being anew, the spirit that animates him is simpler,

1007
01:20:35,416 --> 01:20:36,540
- 更纯粹... - 纯粹?
- purer-- - Purer?

1008
01:20:36,541 --> 01:20:38,541
比普通人更纯粹?
Purer than that of the common man?

1009
01:20:43,291 --> 01:20:44,874
说不定是不受原罪束缚的造物主
What if, unrestrained by sin,

1010
01:20:44,875 --> 01:20:47,874
把气息直接吹进受伤的肉体?
our creator's breath came into its wounded flesh directly?

1011
01:20:47,875 --> 01:20:49,958
老天爷,伊莉莎白
Good God, Elizabeth.

1012
01:20:51,916 --> 01:20:53,957
若要硬逼我自己相信这番话
If I could force myself to believe it,

1013
01:20:53,958 --> 01:20:58,124
我会不禁认为,你对那东西有好感
it would be my inclination to see attraction in you for that thing.

1014
01:20:58,125 --> 01:20:59,625
这是同理心
Understanding.

1015
01:21:00,500 --> 01:21:01,832
我在那对眼眸中看见痛苦
In those eyes I saw pain,

1016
01:21:01,833 --> 01:21:04,040
若痛苦不是智慧的证明 不然是什么?
and what is pain if not evidence of intelligence?

1017
01:21:04,041 --> 01:21:05,665
那我的痛苦呢?
What about my pain?

1018
01:21:05,666 --> 01:21:07,291
你拒绝我的情意呢?
What about what you have denied me?

1019
01:21:09,041 --> 01:21:10,625
我心的渴望...
What my heart wants...

1020
01:21:11,875 --> 01:21:12,916
你的心?
Your heart?

1021
01:21:16,333 --> 01:21:17,790
在人体解剖学中
Of all the human anatomy,

1022
01:21:17,791 --> 01:21:20,416
那是你最不了解的器官
that is the organ furthest from your understanding.

1023
01:21:21,250 --> 01:21:23,208
唯有怪物妄想操控生命,男爵
Only monsters play God, Baron.

1024
01:21:29,250 --> 01:21:31,250
你比普通人更纯粹?
Purer than the common man, hmm?

1025
01:21:36,458 --> 01:21:38,625
而我莫名其妙成了坏人
And I, somehow, the villain. Mm-hmm.

1026
01:21:40,791 --> 01:21:42,625
你的心很纯粹?
Your heart is pure?

1027
01:21:43,333 --> 01:21:45,290
绝对没有
I assure you it isn't.

1028
01:21:45,291 --> 01:21:47,208
我最清楚,因为那是我放的
I should know. I put it there.

1029
01:21:48,125 --> 01:21:48,958
上去
Up.

1030
01:21:59,833 --> 01:22:01,000
再试一次
Let us try again.

1031
01:22:04,250 --> 01:22:05,333
现在把腿伸出来
Now give me your leg.

1032
01:22:06,208 --> 01:22:07,333
腿!
Leg!

1033
01:22:08,458 --> 01:22:09,458
把腿伸出来!
Give me your leg!

1034
01:22:10,416 --> 01:22:12,833
痛苦是智慧的证明,对吧?
Pain is evidence of intelligence, is it not?

1035
01:22:13,416 --> 01:22:14,958
那就来检验这个理论
Well, let's test the theory.

1036
01:22:15,708 --> 01:22:17,541
把腿伸出来!
Give me your leg!

1037
01:22:18,541 --> 01:22:19,458
腿!
Leg!

1038
01:22:20,208 --> 01:22:21,249
腿!
Leg!

1039
01:22:21,250 --> 01:22:22,333
快点!
Come on!

1040
01:22:23,041 --> 01:22:24,250
伸出来,野兽!
Give it to me, you beast!

1041
01:22:25,833 --> 01:22:28,333
把腿伸出来!
Give me your leg!

1042
01:22:30,291 --> 01:22:31,291
腿!
Leg!

1043
01:22:34,666 --> 01:22:36,125
维多!
Victor!

1044
01:22:37,333 --> 01:22:39,041
维多!
Victor!

1045
01:22:41,416 --> 01:22:46,333
维多!
Victor! Victor!

1046
01:22:46,958 --> 01:22:48,000
维多,什么事?
What is it, Victor?

1047
01:22:49,375 --> 01:22:50,333
过来
Come. Come.

1048
01:22:51,625 --> 01:22:54,000
我失败了,我铸下大错
I failed. I made a mistake.

1049
01:22:54,708 --> 01:22:56,874
- 你没失败,我看过你的报告 - 我有
- No, you didn't fail. I saw your papers. - I did.

1050
01:22:56,875 --> 01:22:58,832
- 牠很完美 - 那怪物危险至极
- It's perfect. - The Creature is extremely dangerous.

1051
01:22:58,833 --> 01:23:00,666
没有...维多
There's not... Victor.

1052
01:23:01,375 --> 01:23:02,999
等哈兰德到了之后一起讨论
Let's wait for Harlander and discuss together.

1053
01:23:03,000 --> 01:23:05,583
威廉,有件事应该让你知道
William, there is something you should know.

1054
01:23:06,333 --> 01:23:07,666
我得让你看一个东西
Something I have to show you.

1055
01:23:13,583 --> 01:23:16,416
- 哈兰德... - 他一怒之下杀了哈兰德
- Ha-- Harlander... - In a fit of rage, he killed him.

1056
01:23:22,750 --> 01:23:25,916
你现在知道我为何犹豫不说了吗?
Do you understand now why I was hesitant to share this with you?

1057
01:23:26,541 --> 01:23:28,250
而且绝对不能告诉伊莉莎白
And certainly not with Elizabeth.

1058
01:23:31,750 --> 01:23:33,541
那现在该怎么办?
S... So what's to be done now?

1059
01:23:34,166 --> 01:23:34,999
什么?
What?

1060
01:23:35,000 --> 01:23:36,707
- 接着怎么办? -「接着怎么办」?
- What's to be done? - "What's to be done"?

1061
01:23:36,708 --> 01:23:38,874
你必须带伊莉莎白返回维也纳
You must take Elizabeth back to Vienna.

1062
01:23:38,875 --> 01:23:41,832
就说有急事,你们得即刻启程
Tell her something urgent came up and you have to leave immediately.

1063
01:23:41,833 --> 01:23:43,291
一定要瞒着她
Keep her in the dark.

1064
01:23:44,583 --> 01:23:45,583
这是为了保护她
For her own safety.

1065
01:23:46,166 --> 01:23:47,749
你得照我的话做
You have to do as I say.

1066
01:23:47,750 --> 01:23:50,625
我们会尽快回来 但目前此举暂为上策
We'll be back in no time. But for now, this is for the best.

1067
01:23:51,708 --> 01:23:53,958
拜托你上马车吧
Now get in the carriage, please.

1068
01:24:06,833 --> 01:24:08,625
你认为那怪物的寿命有多长?
The Creature, what's its lifespan, you think?

1069
01:24:09,958 --> 01:24:12,666
很短,肯定不久于世
Brief. Very brief, I'm sure.

1070
01:24:59,291 --> 01:25:01,250
我有很不安的预感
I have the most terrible feeling.

1071
01:25:05,208 --> 01:25:06,083
什么预感?
What is it?

1072
01:25:07,708 --> 01:25:09,000
请马车掉头回去
Turn the carriage around.

1073
01:25:10,125 --> 01:25:11,541
你自己去维也纳
You go to Vienna.

1074
01:25:12,875 --> 01:25:15,791
叫马车掉头,不然我就跳车 维多会杀了他
Turn the carriage around or I will jump. He's going to kill him.

1075
01:25:25,500 --> 01:25:26,625
说一个词
Say one word.

1076
01:25:27,166 --> 01:25:28,625
再说一个词,什么都行
One word more. Anything.

1077
01:25:29,625 --> 01:25:30,625
让我饶你一命
Make me save you.

1078
01:25:35,958 --> 01:25:37,000
维多
- Victor. - Mm-hmm.

1079
01:25:44,958 --> 01:25:47,041
伊莉莎白
Elizabeth.

1080
01:26:27,500 --> 01:26:31,708
维多!
Victor! Victor!

1081
01:26:36,708 --> 01:26:41,875
维多!
Victor!
Victor!

1082
01:27:31,500 --> 01:27:33,957
但事情并未就此结束
But that was not the end of it.

1083
01:27:33,958 --> 01:27:37,291
我想寻求生命,却创造了死亡
In seeking life, I created death.

1084
01:27:43,375 --> 01:27:46,000
看来我得再劝劝我的船员
It would seem I need to address my men again.

1085
01:27:50,583 --> 01:27:51,416
放心吧
Don't worry.

1086
01:27:52,000 --> 01:27:52,958
他们会听我的话
They'll listen to me.

1087
01:27:57,166 --> 01:28:00,874
不要,住手!别伤害他!我在这里
No, no, stop!
Do not harm him! I'm here.

1088
01:28:00,875 --> 01:28:02,250
抓我吧
Take me.

1089
01:28:02,916 --> 01:28:04,082
动手吧,野兽
Go on, beast.

1090
01:28:04,083 --> 01:28:08,041
杀了我俩,证明你制造者的故事无误
Kill us both. Confirm your maker's tale.

1091
01:28:13,541 --> 01:28:18,500
我的制造者...说了他的故事
My maker... told his tale.

1092
01:28:23,833 --> 01:28:26,708
那我也要说出我的故事
Then I will tell you mine.

1093
01:28:30,208 --> 01:28:33,166
(第二部:怪物的故事)

1094
01:28:42,833 --> 01:28:48,415
维多!
Victor! Victor! Victor!

1095
01:28:48,416 --> 01:28:53,208
我叫你的名字,发现只有我一个人
I called your name and understood I was alone.

1096
01:32:52,833 --> 01:32:54,207
- 那是什么? - 射牠!
- What is that? - Shoot at it!

1097
01:32:54,208 --> 01:32:55,375
杀了牠!
Shoot it!

1098
01:33:01,083 --> 01:33:02,375
射中了吗?
Did you get it?

1099
01:33:03,958 --> 01:33:04,958
嘿!

1100
01:33:05,666 --> 01:33:06,875
牠跑去哪了?
Where is it?

1101
01:33:27,125 --> 01:33:29,041
我的伤口痊愈了
My wounds had healed.

1102
01:33:31,958 --> 01:33:36,125
可是我觉得冷,非常冷
But I felt cold, so cold.

1103
01:35:08,750 --> 01:35:10,790
- 生个火吧 - 好
- Can you start the fire? - All right.

1104
01:35:10,791 --> 01:35:12,666
我会尽快把畜栏修好
And I'll repair the corral as soon as I can.

1105
01:35:19,625 --> 01:35:20,999
你们没事吧?杀掉牠了吗?
You all right, then? Did you get it?

1106
01:35:21,000 --> 01:35:23,415
没有,到处都找遍了 就是找不到那个东西
Nah, we looked everywhere. Couldn't find that thing.

1107
01:35:23,416 --> 01:35:25,124
我们明明射中两次
Though we shot at it two times.

1108
01:35:25,125 --> 01:35:27,082
血迹到1.6公里外就消失了
Blood trail died about a mile from here.

1109
01:35:27,083 --> 01:35:29,250
好了,进来吧
All right. Come in. Come in.

1110
01:35:30,000 --> 01:35:31,874
我们追踪了好一会儿
We followed it for a while and then it disappeared. Gone.

1111
01:35:31,875 --> 01:35:33,625
然后牠就消失得无影无踪

1112
01:35:34,500 --> 01:35:36,082
那是什么?是熊吗?
What was it? Was it a bear?

1113
01:35:36,083 --> 01:35:38,374
不是熊,也不是人类
That was no bear or human. I've never seen anything like it.

1114
01:35:38,375 --> 01:35:39,665
我没见过那种东西

1115
01:35:39,666 --> 01:35:40,999
那是鬼吗?
Was it a ghost, then?

1116
01:35:41,000 --> 01:35:44,332
不是,牠会流血,是血肉之躯
It was no ghost. We drew blood. It was flesh and bone.

1117
01:35:44,333 --> 01:35:45,832
来,来这里
Come, come. Over here.

1118
01:35:45,833 --> 01:35:47,165
继续说你看到什么
Tell me more about what you saw.

1119
01:35:47,166 --> 01:35:50,124
安娜玛丽亚,带爷爷去壁炉边
Anna-Maria, take your grandfather over by the fireplace.

1120
01:35:50,125 --> 01:35:51,750
确保他感到舒适
Make sure he's comfortable.

1121
01:35:52,833 --> 01:35:54,166
这里,爷爷
Over here, Grandfather.

1122
01:35:56,458 --> 01:35:58,708
我们追到森林深处,怎么都找不到
We went deep into the forest. Couldn't find it.

1123
01:36:04,666 --> 01:36:06,040
我们会逮到牠的
We will get it.

1124
01:36:06,041 --> 01:36:07,708
- 要花点时间 - 对
- It'll take time. - Yeah.

1125
01:36:08,666 --> 01:36:10,832
安娜玛丽亚,过来
Anna-Maria, come.

1126
01:36:10,833 --> 01:36:12,875
过来,宝贝,来外面帮我忙
Come, love. Help me outside.

1127
01:36:23,541 --> 01:36:25,416
我被那个老人所打动
The old man moved me.

1128
01:36:29,833 --> 01:36:32,791
他失明的双眼充满智慧
And his unseeing eyes were full of wisdom.

1129
01:36:45,541 --> 01:36:47,791
这些人拥有一种声音
These people possessed a sound.

1130
01:36:49,125 --> 01:36:50,749
用来告诉彼此
Used it to tell each other

1131
01:36:50,750 --> 01:36:54,541
感受和想法
about feelings and ideas.

1132
01:36:56,208 --> 01:36:58,458
他们称之为词语
They called them words.

1133
01:37:01,750 --> 01:37:02,833
专心点
Pay attention.

1134
01:37:03,708 --> 01:37:04,625
这是什么?
What is this?

1135
01:37:05,208 --> 01:37:06,208
男生
A boy.

1136
01:37:07,458 --> 01:37:09,250
- 再说一次 - 男生
- And again. - A boy.

1137
01:37:10,250 --> 01:37:11,541
非常好,孩子
Very good, my child.

1138
01:37:12,833 --> 01:37:13,915
那这个呢?
And this?

1139
01:37:13,916 --> 01:37:16,041
是...眼睛
An... An eye.

1140
01:37:16,833 --> 01:37:18,624
- 再说一次 - 眼睛
- And again. - An eye.

1141
01:37:18,625 --> 01:37:21,749
非常好,乖孙女
Yeah. Well done. Well done, my girl.

1142
01:37:21,750 --> 01:37:23,832
- 眼睛 - 这个呢?
- Eye. - And this one?

1143
01:37:23,833 --> 01:37:24,832
手
The hand.

1144
01:37:24,833 --> 01:37:26,750
- 非常好 - 手
- Very good. - Hand.

1145
01:37:27,791 --> 01:37:28,749
来帮个忙
Give us a hand.

1146
01:37:28,750 --> 01:37:31,207
拿绳子把后面最粗的那根绑起来
Tie a rope around the biggest one back there.

1147
01:37:31,208 --> 01:37:33,708
我向往加入这个家庭
I longed to be part of this family.

1148
01:37:34,375 --> 01:37:36,415
冬天来临前,家里需要更多引火柴
We'll need more kindling before the winter.

1149
01:37:36,416 --> 01:37:38,582
我们会出去张罗几趟
We'll take a few trips.

1150
01:37:38,583 --> 01:37:40,583
成为他们的帮手
To be their benefactor.

1151
01:37:41,166 --> 01:37:42,665
房屋需要更粗大的树干
We'll need larger trunks for the structure.

1152
01:37:42,666 --> 01:37:43,582
好
All right.

1153
01:37:43,583 --> 01:37:46,750
我究竟能为他们做什么?
What could I possibly do for them?

1154
01:37:52,333 --> 01:37:55,290
安娜玛丽亚!父亲!
Anna-Maria! Father!

1155
01:37:55,291 --> 01:37:57,625
来!快来看!
Come! Come and see!

1156
01:37:59,541 --> 01:38:01,207
你看,安娜玛丽亚!
Look, Anna-Maria!

1157
01:38:01,208 --> 01:38:03,000
看啊,还有更多!快看!
Look, there's more! Look!

1158
01:38:05,083 --> 01:38:06,875
谁会这么好心?
Who could have done this?

1159
01:38:09,916 --> 01:38:11,708
是森林精灵
The Spirit of the Forest.

1160
01:38:13,333 --> 01:38:14,583
我们应该感谢他
We should thank him.

1161
01:38:16,333 --> 01:38:17,374
谢谢你
Thank you.

1162
01:38:17,375 --> 01:38:20,165
说「谢谢,森林精灵」
Say, "Thank you, Spirit of the Forest."

1163
01:38:20,166 --> 01:38:23,290
谢谢,森林精灵
Thank you. Thank you, Spirit of the Forest.

1164
01:38:23,291 --> 01:38:24,375
谢谢
Thank you.

1165
01:38:25,416 --> 01:38:27,125
过来,看这边
Come. Look over here.

1166
01:38:33,541 --> 01:38:34,583
谢谢
Thank you.

1167
01:38:36,666 --> 01:38:40,749
那一刻起,我成了他们无形的守护者
From then on, I became their invisible guardian.

1168
01:38:40,750 --> 01:38:43,957
森林精灵
The Spirit of the Forest.

1169
01:38:43,958 --> 01:38:49,333
他们偶尔也会对我聊表心意
And on occasion, they too extended a small kindness towards me.

1170
01:38:50,375 --> 01:38:52,583
衣物、面包
Clothes, bread.

1171
01:38:54,791 --> 01:38:56,291
有一段时间
And for a moment,

1172
01:38:57,375 --> 01:39:00,458
极其短暂的时间
a brief, brief moment,

1173
01:39:01,250 --> 01:39:03,583
我和世界和平共处
the world and I were at peace.

1174
01:39:11,750 --> 01:39:13,332
跟上去
Come along. Come along.

1175
01:39:13,333 --> 01:39:14,290
进去,没错
In you go. Yeah.

1176
01:39:14,291 --> 01:39:15,749
一定要关好栅门
Make sure you close that gate.

1177
01:39:15,750 --> 01:39:17,624
谁会这么帮忙?
Who could have done this?

1178
01:39:17,625 --> 01:39:19,833
是森林精灵,对吧?
The Spirit of the Forest, eh?

1179
01:39:21,125 --> 01:39:22,125
交给我吧
I got it.

1180
01:39:24,125 --> 01:39:28,832
「最后,那名自傲的年轻人」
"And in the end, the proud young man

1181
01:39:28,833 --> 01:39:32,124
「再也找不到他失去的手」
could never find his missing hand."

1182
01:39:32,125 --> 01:39:36,374
「手化成石头,他财产没了」
"It turned to stone, his fortune gone,

1183
01:39:36,375 --> 01:39:40,041
「他失去自尊,还有土地」
and he lost his pride and lost his land."

1184
01:39:46,125 --> 01:39:48,207
非常好,亲爱的
Very good, my dear.

1185
01:39:48,208 --> 01:39:51,250
念得很好,换这本
Beautifully read. Now try this one.

1186
01:40:01,333 --> 01:40:02,458
是野狼
Wolves.

1187
01:40:47,750 --> 01:40:48,750
有个想法
An idea,

1188
01:40:50,041 --> 01:40:52,333
有种感觉在我心中成形
a feeling became clear to me.

1189
01:40:54,958 --> 01:40:57,583
猎人并不痛恨野狼
The hunter did not hate the wolf.

1190
01:40:58,375 --> 01:41:00,750
野狼也不痛恨绵羊
The wolf did not hate the sheep.

1191
01:41:06,458 --> 01:41:09,666
但三者间似乎必然会发生暴力
But violence felt inevitable between them.

1192
01:41:10,375 --> 01:41:15,583
我心想:「也许这就是世道吧」
Perhaps, I thought, this was the way of the world.

1193
01:41:16,708 --> 01:41:20,375
你会被追捕和杀害
It would hunt you and kill you

1194
01:41:21,125 --> 01:41:23,791
单纯是因为你的身分
just for being who you are.

1195
01:41:26,250 --> 01:41:28,583
我们月底要去卖绵羊,父亲
The sheep will be sold by the end of the month, Father.

1196
01:41:29,291 --> 01:41:31,958
到时我会带你、艾玛 和安娜玛丽亚一起进城
Then I'll take you, Alma and Anna-Maria into town.

1197
01:41:32,750 --> 01:41:33,874
我们会进入山区
We'll go into the mountains,

1198
01:41:33,875 --> 01:41:36,040
猎杀野狼,在冬天结束时返回
hunt the wolves and be back at the end of winter.

1199
01:41:36,041 --> 01:41:38,915
我冬天都在此独居祈祷
I pray here alone every winter and this year will be no different.

1200
01:41:38,916 --> 01:41:41,082
今年也不例外

1201
01:41:41,083 --> 01:41:43,874
求求你,父亲,明理一点
Please, Father, listen to reason.

1202
01:41:43,875 --> 01:41:47,375
你们就忙你们的,我也是
You do what you must and so will I.

1203
01:41:51,208 --> 01:41:52,541
你这个老顽固
You stubborn old goat.

1204
01:41:55,291 --> 01:41:57,666
现在只有我和你了,精灵
It's just you and I now, Spirit.

1205
01:41:58,500 --> 01:42:00,000
只有我和你了
Just you and I.

1206
01:42:00,625 --> 01:42:05,249
我脑海中想像过许许多多种
And I had formed in my imagination many ways

1207
01:42:05,250 --> 01:42:08,000
在老人面前现身的方式
I would present myself to the old man.

1208
01:42:09,666 --> 01:42:11,041
他会怕我吗?
Would he fear me?

1209
01:42:12,458 --> 01:42:13,625
欢迎我?
Welcome me?

1210
01:42:15,083 --> 01:42:16,291
还是下逐客令?
Turn me away?

1211
01:42:23,791 --> 01:42:25,250
谁在那里?
Who goes there?

1212
01:42:30,958 --> 01:42:35,083
往前一步,我踏进了不同的世界
With a single step, I entered a different world.

1213
01:42:36,416 --> 01:42:38,958
我以前只能远远看着
One I had only seen from afar.

1214
01:42:41,250 --> 01:42:42,958
请问你是谁?
Please, who is it?

1215
01:42:43,583 --> 01:42:44,583
回答我
Answer me.

1216
01:42:45,958 --> 01:42:46,833
告诉我
Tell me.

1217
01:42:47,458 --> 01:42:48,958
你为何会来这里?
Why are you here?

1218
01:42:51,416 --> 01:42:52,250
旅行
Travel.

1219
01:42:52,833 --> 01:42:54,625
欢迎你,亲爱的旅人
Welcome, dear traveler.

1220
01:42:55,500 --> 01:42:58,290
我很感激你的陪伴
Do not think me ungrateful for the company if I ask you to procure a chair.

1221
01:42:58,291 --> 01:43:01,457
只是你得自己找椅子坐

1222
01:43:01,458 --> 01:43:06,415
我当不了称职的主人
I... I find it difficult being a good host.

1223
01:43:06,416 --> 01:43:11,041
没错,因为我看不见
Yes.
My... My sight has failed me.

1224
01:43:12,708 --> 01:43:16,707
不过桌上有面包和白兰地
But there is bread and brandy on the table.

1225
01:43:16,708 --> 01:43:17,916
请自行取用
Pray help yourself.

1226
01:43:20,125 --> 01:43:21,833
白兰...地?
Bran... dy?

1227
01:43:23,208 --> 01:43:24,957
你的语言
Your language.

1228
01:43:24,958 --> 01:43:28,832
你讲得不太流利
You have a hard time speaking it.

1229
01:43:28,833 --> 01:43:31,000
你不是本地人吗?
Are you not from these parts?

1230
01:43:36,750 --> 01:43:37,750
你在害怕吗?
Are you afraid?

1231
01:43:39,750 --> 01:43:41,000
不用怕
No need to be.

1232
01:43:45,916 --> 01:43:47,541
你在怕什么?
What are you afraid of?

1233
01:43:48,291 --> 01:43:49,333
什么都怕
- Everything. - Your...

1234
01:43:50,833 --> 01:43:53,749
你的手好冰
Your hands are frozen

1235
01:43:53,750 --> 01:43:57,499
而且还受伤了,对吧?
and you've been hurt, have you not?

1236
01:43:57,500 --> 01:43:58,457
受伤?
Hurt?

1237
01:43:58,458 --> 01:44:05,290
对,你的手和脸上都有伤疤
Yes. Your hands and face have scars

1238
01:44:05,291 --> 01:44:06,833
而且你身穿制服
and you are wearing uniform.

1239
01:44:07,458 --> 01:44:09,291
你在打仗时受伤吗?
Were you injured in battle?

1240
01:44:11,833 --> 01:44:13,000
你之前都躲在
You were hiding

1241
01:44:14,125 --> 01:44:16,541
磨坊齿轮房,对吧?
in the mill gears, were you not?

1242
01:44:21,125 --> 01:44:24,207
我就知道,森林精灵
Ah!
Yeah. Yeah. The Spirit of the Forest.

1243
01:44:24,208 --> 01:44:25,208
是的
Yes.

1244
01:44:26,083 --> 01:44:28,541
虽然我看不见你的模样
I cannot judge of your countenance,

1245
01:44:29,375 --> 01:44:31,665
但你的声音中有股特质
but there is something in your voice

1246
01:44:31,666 --> 01:44:36,082
让我相信你善良又仁慈
which persuades me of your goodwill and kindness.

1247
01:44:36,083 --> 01:44:37,125
仁慈?
- Kindness? - Mm.

1248
01:44:39,666 --> 01:44:41,750
留下来陪我
Stay with me.

1249
01:44:43,083 --> 01:44:46,082
跟我一起用餐和取暖
Share my food and fire.

1250
01:44:46,083 --> 01:44:50,040
我很乐意跟你分享我微薄的物资
I would be delighted to share what little I have with you

1251
01:44:50,041 --> 01:44:53,541
也会很高兴有你相伴
and would be greatly helped by your companionship.

1252
01:44:54,375 --> 01:44:57,874
而且你可以念书给我听
And you... you could read to me.

1253
01:44:57,875 --> 01:44:59,000
念书?
- Read? - Mm.

1254
01:45:00,166 --> 01:45:05,916
把这里当自己家,把我当成你的朋友
Make this your home and I your friend.

1255
01:45:07,583 --> 01:45:08,458
朋友
Friend.

1256
01:45:13,916 --> 01:45:14,916
朋友
Friend.

1257
01:45:23,375 --> 01:45:24,208
朋友
Friends.

1258
01:45:25,625 --> 01:45:29,750
我就是在那时读到第一个故事
And it was then that I read my first story,

1259
01:45:30,666 --> 01:45:33,333
那是开天辟地的第一个故事
and it was the first story.

1260
01:45:34,416 --> 01:45:39,541
我读到男人亚当和女人夏娃
I read about a man named Adam and a woman named Eve,

1261
01:45:40,250 --> 01:45:44,415
他们在第一个园子的时光
about their time in the first garden.

1262
01:45:44,416 --> 01:45:47,999
我读到敌对城市的兴起
I read about the rise of rival cities

1263
01:45:48,000 --> 01:45:49,958
一座倒塌的塔
and the collapse of a tower

1264
01:45:50,458 --> 01:45:52,749
还有天神的愤怒
and the wrath of a God.

1265
01:45:52,750 --> 01:45:57,624
我读到人对抗恶龙
And I read about men that fought dragons

1266
01:45:57,625 --> 01:46:00,541
以及他们失去一切
and men who lost everything.

1267
01:46:01,416 --> 01:46:02,958
时光流逝
And time passed

1268
01:46:03,666 --> 01:46:06,916
随着秋叶凋零而远去
and fell away with the leaves of autumn.

1269
01:46:18,583 --> 01:46:21,708
亲爱的朋友,你没看过雪吗?
Have you never seen the snow, my dear friend?

1270
01:46:23,333 --> 01:46:27,125
它使世界洁净如洗...宛若新生
It makes the world clean... and new.

1271
01:46:33,041 --> 01:46:38,332
「『吾乃奥西曼迪斯,王中之王』」
"My name is Ozymandias, King of Kings."

1272
01:46:38,333 --> 01:46:41,833
「『观吾之伟业 豪杰如汝,亦当自愧弗如』」
"Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair."

1273
01:46:43,000 --> 01:46:45,250
「巨像残骸四周」
"No thing beside remains."

1274
01:46:45,791 --> 01:46:50,082
「空无一物,唯见无际的荒凉」
"Round the decay of that colossal wreck, boundless and bare."

1275
01:46:50,083 --> 01:46:53,833
「平沙寂寂,绵延至天涯」
"The lone and level sands stretch far away."

1276
01:46:55,541 --> 01:46:58,833
「吾乃奥西曼迪斯...」
"My name is Ozymandias..."

1277
01:47:05,166 --> 01:47:07,750
除了这些,世上还有其他书吗?
Are there more books than this in the world?

1278
01:47:09,791 --> 01:47:11,666
肯定还有一些
A few more, I'm sure.

1279
01:47:12,416 --> 01:47:13,833
这里没有了
Not here.

1280
01:47:15,875 --> 01:47:18,875
左边最后一本,去拿吧
Last book on the left. Take it.

1281
01:47:19,375 --> 01:47:21,000
我们还没读那本书
We haven't got to it.

1282
01:47:21,500 --> 01:47:24,249
《失乐园》,米尔顿着
Paradise Lost, Milton.

1283
01:47:24,250 --> 01:47:27,250
人类有问题想问神
Man has questions for God.

1284
01:47:28,000 --> 01:47:30,250
连神自己也有疑问
Even God has questions.

1285
01:47:31,041 --> 01:47:32,790
祂应该是想知道答案
I think he wanted answers and that is why he sent us his son.

1286
01:47:32,791 --> 01:47:35,791
才会派儿子到凡间

1287
01:47:36,333 --> 01:47:38,791
祂大概是对死亡感兴趣吧
Death probably intrigued him.

1288
01:47:39,458 --> 01:47:40,333
苦难
Suffering.

1289
01:47:41,500 --> 01:47:44,458
我想知道我是谁
I want to know who I am.

1290
01:47:45,166 --> 01:47:47,415
我从何而来?
Where do I come from?

1291
01:47:47,416 --> 01:47:49,415
神夺走你的记忆
God took your memory just as I wish he would take mine away.

1292
01:47:49,416 --> 01:47:52,791
我也希望祂夺走我的

1293
01:47:54,250 --> 01:47:57,541
多年以前,我曾杀死一个人
Many years ago, I took a man's life.

1294
01:47:58,208 --> 01:47:59,125
一个好人
A good man.

1295
01:47:59,666 --> 01:48:02,083
从此,我便赎罪至今
And I have been atoning for it since.

1296
01:48:04,375 --> 01:48:05,250
原谅
Forgive.

1297
01:48:06,166 --> 01:48:07,000
遗忘
Forget.

1298
01:48:07,708 --> 01:48:09,625
这是衡量智慧的真正准则
The true measure of wisdom.

1299
01:48:10,833 --> 01:48:12,957
知道你受到伤害
To know you have been harmed,

1300
01:48:12,958 --> 01:48:15,207
以及谁伤害你
by whom you have been harmed,

1301
01:48:15,208 --> 01:48:18,166
并选择释怀
and choose to let it all fade.

1302
01:48:19,250 --> 01:48:23,207
但我无法忘记我不记得的事
But I cannot forget what I cannot remember.

1303
01:48:23,208 --> 01:48:24,708
你什么都想不起来吗?
Do you recall nothing?

1304
01:48:30,166 --> 01:48:32,875
在我的梦中...
In my dreams...

1305
01:48:35,666 --> 01:48:38,916
我...看见回忆
...I... see memories.

1306
01:48:42,250 --> 01:48:43,791
都是不同的人
Different men.

1307
01:48:46,250 --> 01:48:49,000
全都...支离破碎的
All... pieces.

1308
01:48:55,958 --> 01:48:57,041
我...
I...

1309
01:48:59,250 --> 01:49:03,125
我记得火和水
I remember f... fire and water.

1310
01:49:06,208 --> 01:49:08,208
还有脚底的沙子
And sand under my feet.

1311
01:49:15,375 --> 01:49:16,625
还有一个词
And a word.

1312
01:49:19,291 --> 01:49:20,791
就一个词
A single word.

1313
01:49:23,250 --> 01:49:24,541
什么词?
What is it?

1314
01:49:27,333 --> 01:49:28,333
维多
Victor.

1315
01:49:29,625 --> 01:49:30,791
去找吧
Go to it.

1316
01:49:31,750 --> 01:49:32,958
找那个词
The word.

1317
01:50:09,791 --> 01:50:11,833
然后我得知始末
And then I learned it.

1318
01:50:12,750 --> 01:50:14,958
骇人的真相
The horror of the truth.

1319
01:50:20,791 --> 01:50:23,916
我知道我什么都不是
I understood that I was nothing.

1320
01:50:25,208 --> 01:50:26,583
只是个可怜人
A wretch.

1321
01:50:27,125 --> 01:50:28,416
一块污渍
A blot.

1322
01:50:28,958 --> 01:50:32,083
跟人类的本质完全不同
Not even of the same nature as man.

1323
01:50:35,416 --> 01:50:37,666
这个伤痛在我心头萦绕
This hurt clung to my mind.

1324
01:50:39,791 --> 01:50:41,500
挥之不去
It never let go.

1325
01:51:24,916 --> 01:51:26,500
然后我看到了
Then I saw it.

1326
01:51:28,125 --> 01:51:29,500
你的名字
Your name.

1327
01:51:30,250 --> 01:51:33,665
「维多弗兰肯斯坦」
"Victor Frankenstein."

1328
01:51:33,666 --> 01:51:35,791
还有你在哪里
And where to find you.

1329
01:51:57,041 --> 01:51:58,291
不要!
No!

1330
01:51:59,541 --> 01:52:01,291
不要!
No!

1331
01:53:10,208 --> 01:53:11,707
你回来了
You came back.

1332
01:53:11,708 --> 01:53:14,166
我发现自己是什么了
I found what I am.

1333
01:53:18,333 --> 01:53:20,750
还有制造我的材料
What I am made from.

1334
01:53:23,375 --> 01:53:28,000
我是...一堆尸首的后代
I am... the child of a charnel house.

1335
01:53:31,416 --> 01:53:32,750
一具残骸
A wreckage.

1336
01:53:33,875 --> 01:53:37,291
用废料和弃尸拼凑而成
Assembled from refuse and the discarded dead.

1337
01:53:43,916 --> 01:53:45,125
一只怪物
A monster.

1338
01:53:46,666 --> 01:53:48,958
我知道你是什么
I know what you are.

1339
01:53:51,208 --> 01:53:52,333
一个好人
A good man.

1340
01:53:53,208 --> 01:53:57,708
而且...你是我的朋友
And... you are my friend.

1341
01:54:07,500 --> 01:54:08,666
朋友?
Friend?

1342
01:54:10,500 --> 01:54:11,666
朋友
Friend.

1343
01:54:14,916 --> 01:54:15,958
那是什么?
What is that thing?

1344
01:54:17,875 --> 01:54:19,625
是林子里那个东西吗?
The-- The thing from the woods?

1345
01:54:20,375 --> 01:54:22,083
你对他做了什么事?
What have you done to him?

1346
01:54:24,416 --> 01:54:25,375
别动
Don't move.

1347
01:54:36,750 --> 01:54:39,083
快点!装子弹!杀了牠!
Quick! Reload! Kill it!

1348
01:55:53,000 --> 01:55:55,041
我又陷入寂静之中
There was silence again,

1349
01:55:56,291 --> 01:56:01,541
接着...是无情的生命
and then... merciless life.

1350
01:56:16,958 --> 01:56:19,249
我死了多久?
How long did I die for?

1351
01:56:19,250 --> 01:56:20,750
我不知道
I do not know.

1352
01:56:21,416 --> 01:56:23,708
但我看到身上的伤口复原了
But I saw my injuries healed.

1353
01:56:24,833 --> 01:56:28,458
冬天的冷空气刺痛我的肺
The cold winter air stung in my lungs.

1354
01:56:36,583 --> 01:56:39,708
我感受到前所未有的寂寞
I felt lonelier than ever,

1355
01:56:40,583 --> 01:56:45,500
因为对人类来说 只有一个方法能了结痛苦
because for every man there was but one remedy to all pain:

1356
01:56:46,416 --> 01:56:51,166
死亡,你却连这礼物也不给我
Death, a gift you too had denied me.

1357
01:56:52,125 --> 01:56:54,166
我心中涌起羡慕之情
Envy rose within me

1358
01:56:55,083 --> 01:56:58,083
决定向你提出一个请求
and decided to demand a single grace from you.

1359
01:56:59,416 --> 01:57:01,125
我的创造者
My creator.

1360
01:57:02,458 --> 01:57:07,083
我想要...一个伴侣
I would demand... a companion.

1361
01:57:33,541 --> 01:57:34,958
你得起床了
I need you to get up.

1362
01:57:36,333 --> 01:57:37,915
好,没问题
Yes, of course. Of course.

1363
01:57:37,916 --> 01:57:40,791
婚礼快开始了,我要你在我身边
The wedding will start soon and I want you by my side.

1364
01:57:41,500 --> 01:57:42,791
要不是你心地善良
It's hard to believe,

1365
01:57:43,750 --> 01:57:45,750
很难相信你也能抱得美人归
if not for your kind nature.

1366
01:58:01,000 --> 01:58:03,375
我跟几个宾客打听了调查进度
I've spoken to a few guests about the inquest.

1367
01:58:04,208 --> 01:58:05,291
关于爆炸案
About the explosion.

1368
01:58:06,958 --> 01:58:09,208
多数人都接受结果了
The majority accept it for what it was.

1369
01:58:11,541 --> 01:58:13,541
所以是什么结果,威廉?
And what was it, William?

1370
01:58:14,958 --> 01:58:16,041
结案了,维多
The past, Victor.

1371
01:58:17,708 --> 01:58:19,000
那是一桩可怕的意外
A terrible accident.

1372
01:58:26,333 --> 01:58:28,166
我打算卖掉庄园
I intend to sell the estate.

1373
01:58:31,583 --> 01:58:33,625
我们只拥有彼此了
All we have is each other.

1374
01:58:49,333 --> 01:58:51,249
我要你们到处撒花瓣
I want you to throw the petals everywhere.

1375
01:58:51,250 --> 01:58:52,750
要遍地都是
Throw them everywhere.

1376
01:58:55,291 --> 01:58:57,041
去楼上给我狠狠撒
Mm.
Go upstairs and do some more of that.

1377
01:59:06,458 --> 01:59:09,916
我知道在仪式前见到新娘不吉利
I know it is bad luck to see the bride before the ceremony.

1378
01:59:10,541 --> 01:59:11,750
只有新郎不能见
Only for the groom.

1379
01:59:13,416 --> 01:59:14,958
说得对,我没差
Yes, that's right. Not for me.

1380
01:59:17,250 --> 01:59:18,458
你好,伊莉莎白
Hello, Elizabeth.

1381
01:59:21,375 --> 01:59:24,875
我以前鲜少后悔,而今却懊恼万分
I've rarely felt remorse before and now I feel little else. I...

1382
01:59:25,583 --> 01:59:29,624
是我痴狂得太久,不过都结束了
A fever gripped me for so long, but it has passed,

1383
01:59:29,625 --> 01:59:31,833
我现在对你没有非分之想
and I see you now as I should.

1384
01:59:33,541 --> 01:59:37,582
无论如何,我都要祝福你和我弟弟
For whatever it's worth, I... I wish you and my little brother,

1385
01:59:37,583 --> 01:59:40,500
而我爱他胜于生命,愿你们幸福圆满
who I love more than life, the very best.

1386
01:59:43,208 --> 01:59:45,166
你自己可能深信不疑
You may like to believe you do.

1387
01:59:49,250 --> 01:59:51,125
你敢说,我是不敢听
And I dread to even hear it.

1388
01:59:55,208 --> 01:59:57,916
我的大喜之日要请你帮个忙
On my wedding day, I ask you but for a single grace.

1389
01:59:59,250 --> 02:00:00,458
别再说谎了
No more lies.

1390
02:00:01,875 --> 02:00:03,790
- 我想告诉你... - 马上离开新娘房
- I-- I want to tell you-- - Leave my chambers now.

1391
02:00:03,791 --> 02:00:06,125
- 伊莉莎白 - 出去!
- Elizabeth. - Leave!

1392
02:01:00,166 --> 02:01:02,125
从阴影中走出来
Come out of the shadows,

1393
02:01:03,125 --> 02:01:04,500
如果你在这里
if you are here.

1394
02:01:21,958 --> 02:01:23,208
你是来感谢我的吗?
Are you here to thank me?

1395
02:01:23,833 --> 02:01:27,375
你大难不死,还聪明到找得到我
You survived and are intelligent enough to have found me.

1396
02:01:29,375 --> 02:01:30,790
我把你造得很好
I made you well.

1397
02:01:30,791 --> 02:01:37,541
我需要你为我制造一个伴侣
I need you to make a companion for me.

1398
02:01:38,166 --> 02:01:40,207
一个像我的人
One like me.

1399
02:01:40,208 --> 02:01:42,458
伴侣?
A com... A companion?

1400
02:01:48,125 --> 02:01:49,125
我懂了
Oh.
I see.

1401
02:01:53,416 --> 02:01:54,750
另一只怪物
Another monster.

1402
02:01:55,416 --> 02:01:56,416
对
Yes.

1403
02:01:57,291 --> 02:01:59,458
我们可以一起当怪物
We can be monsters together.

1404
02:02:03,000 --> 02:02:07,415
我付出惨痛代价才恢复理性
I have found sanity at such a cost,

1405
02:02:07,416 --> 02:02:11,499
而你...这疯子要我重蹈覆辙
and you here... are madness calling me back.

1406
02:02:11,500 --> 02:02:13,708
我死不了
I cannot die.

1407
02:02:17,333 --> 02:02:19,375
我也无法...
And I cannot live...

1408
02:02:21,916 --> 02:02:22,958
独活
alone.

1409
02:02:24,250 --> 02:02:26,791
你明知道我造出极其恐怖的东西
In you I have created something truly horrible.

1410
02:02:28,041 --> 02:02:30,041
我不是东西
Not something.

1411
02:02:30,958 --> 02:02:32,791
是人
Someone.

1412
02:02:33,625 --> 02:02:37,000
你造了一个人
You made someone.

1413
02:02:37,708 --> 02:02:38,625
我
Me.

1414
02:02:39,541 --> 02:02:42,333
就算我是个谜,创造者,我会思考
Whatever puzzle I am, creator, I think.

1415
02:02:43,208 --> 02:02:44,458
我有感受
I feel.

1416
02:02:45,958 --> 02:02:47,666
我有一个小请求...
I have this sole petition...

1417
02:02:48,541 --> 02:02:52,625
制造一个像我这样的人
Make one like me.

1418
02:02:54,375 --> 02:02:55,500
然后呢?
And then what?

1419
02:02:56,583 --> 02:02:58,291
生殖
Procreation.

1420
02:03:00,083 --> 02:03:01,708
繁衍
Reproduction.
Mm...

1421
02:03:06,541 --> 02:03:07,708
成家?
A home?

1422
02:03:08,625 --> 02:03:10,041
丧礼?
A grave?

1423
02:03:11,625 --> 02:03:15,332
死亡繁衍死亡,又再繁衍死亡
Death begetting death begetting death.

1424
02:03:15,333 --> 02:03:17,499
恶魔种族在世间开枝散叶
A race of devils propagated upon the earth.

1425
02:03:17,500 --> 02:03:19,708
发泄淫欲,自行繁殖后代
Obscenity perpetuating itself.

1426
02:03:20,500 --> 02:03:23,957
你当我淫兽,但我只是人罢了
I am obscene to you, but to myself I simply am.

1427
02:03:23,958 --> 02:03:25,291
给我滚!
Begone!

1428
02:03:27,625 --> 02:03:33,916
我再也不会造出你这种邪恶的畸形物
Never again will I make something like you, wicked and deformed.

1429
02:03:38,375 --> 02:03:44,416
结果仍是你的意志至上,维多
Then it is still all about your will, Victor.

1430
02:03:47,125 --> 02:03:52,458
赐给我生命又谴责我的可怕意志?
Hmm?
That horrible, horrible will that birthed me condemns me now?

1431
02:03:53,833 --> 02:03:58,458
我会说话不是奇迹,你会聆听才是!
The miracle is not that I should speak, but that you would ever listen!

1432
02:04:02,166 --> 02:04:04,832
如果你不给我爱
If you are not to award me love, then I will indulge in rage.

1433
02:04:04,833 --> 02:04:07,415
我将怒火冲天

1434
02:04:07,416 --> 02:04:09,875
而且永不止息
And mine is infinite.

1435
02:04:15,166 --> 02:04:16,582
借过
Step aside.

1436
02:04:16,583 --> 02:04:17,625
维多
Victor.

1437
02:04:19,000 --> 02:04:20,041
怎么回事?
What's going on?

1438
02:04:38,833 --> 02:04:39,875
你...
You...

1439
02:04:44,833 --> 02:04:45,708
你...
You...

1440
02:04:46,708 --> 02:04:47,625
是你
It's you.

1441
02:04:52,791 --> 02:04:55,166
伊莉莎白,离牠远一点!
Elizabeth, move away from it!

1442
02:04:55,791 --> 02:04:56,708
不要!
No!

1443
02:05:10,958 --> 02:05:13,791
牠攻击她!
It attacked her! It attacked her!

1444
02:05:33,291 --> 02:05:34,833
带我跟你走
Take me with you.

1445
02:05:48,833 --> 02:05:50,666
我的天哪!
Oh, my God!

1446
02:06:16,291 --> 02:06:18,540
不行,让我...我会救你
No, let me... I can save you.

1447
02:06:18,541 --> 02:06:19,750
我会救你
I can save you.

1448
02:06:20,333 --> 02:06:21,333
是什么要害我?
From what?

1449
02:06:22,791 --> 02:06:23,916
你吗?
From you?

1450
02:06:25,416 --> 02:06:26,790
我怕你,维多
I fear you, Victor.

1451
02:06:26,791 --> 02:06:27,999
别说了...
No, no...

1452
02:06:28,000 --> 02:06:29,707
从小就很怕
I always have.

1453
02:06:29,708 --> 02:06:32,500
每一丁点疯狂和毁灭
Every ounce of madness and destruction.

1454
02:06:33,750 --> 02:06:37,333
吞噬万物的猛火烈焰
The very conflagration that devoured everything.

1455
02:06:39,166 --> 02:06:40,541
都是来自于你
It all came from you.

1456
02:06:46,541 --> 02:06:48,041
你才是怪物
You are the monster.

1457
02:07:21,125 --> 02:07:23,291
我在这世界从来没有归属感
My place was never in this world.

1458
02:07:25,166 --> 02:07:29,750
我曾寻找过一份难以言喻的渴望
I sought and longed for something I could not quite name.

1459
02:07:31,666 --> 02:07:33,541
但我在你身上找到了
But in you, I found it.

1460
02:07:36,833 --> 02:07:39,291
失而复得
To be lost and to be found,

1461
02:07:40,291 --> 02:07:42,291
正是爱的寿命
that is the lifespan of love.

1462
02:07:44,291 --> 02:07:45,708
纵然转瞬即逝
And in its brevity,

1463
02:07:46,875 --> 02:07:48,208
以悲剧告终...
its tragedy...

1464
02:07:52,291 --> 02:07:54,125
却因此永垂不朽
this has been made eternal.

1465
02:07:57,916 --> 02:08:01,333
就此离去...也算无憾
Better this way... to fade...

1466
02:08:03,375 --> 02:08:05,625
因为有你凝视着我
with your eyes gazing upon me.

1467
02:08:48,291 --> 02:08:51,375
她走了,我想随她而去
She is gone and I long to follow.

1468
02:08:56,041 --> 02:08:58,333
你赐给我生命,非我所愿
You gave me life unwanted.

1469
02:08:59,625 --> 02:09:01,500
我要归还给你
I give that back to you.

1470
02:09:02,291 --> 02:09:04,208
你当我是怪物
You thought me a monster.

1471
02:09:05,041 --> 02:09:07,041
现在我要回敬你
Now I return the favor.

1472
02:09:12,708 --> 02:09:15,375
杀了我!现在就动手杀了我吧!
Kill me! Kill me now, do it!

1473
02:09:16,416 --> 02:09:18,291
我会让你流血
I will make you bleed.

1474
02:09:19,125 --> 02:09:21,250
我会使你谦卑
I will make you humble.

1475
02:09:21,916 --> 02:09:23,583
你是我的创造者
You may be my creator,

1476
02:09:24,166 --> 02:09:28,208
但今天起,我是你的主人
but from this day forward, I will be your master.

1477
02:10:08,041 --> 02:10:09,624
你一路追杀我
You hunted me past the forests,

1478
02:10:09,625 --> 02:10:12,416
越过重重森林

1479
02:10:13,083 --> 02:10:15,041
翻山越岭
past the mountains,

1480
02:10:15,666 --> 02:10:18,083
踏破冰封的地平线
past frozen horizons,

1481
02:10:19,125 --> 02:10:22,041
直到一片苍茫
until there was nothing left.

1482
02:10:22,666 --> 02:10:26,083
只剩下你...和我
Just you... and me.

1483
02:10:46,208 --> 02:10:47,125
我需要弹药
I need ammunition.

1484
02:10:50,333 --> 02:10:51,749
把刀磨利
Sharpen this.

1485
02:10:51,750 --> 02:10:54,208
三罐炼乳、木柴
Three cans of condensed milk, some firewood.

1486
02:10:56,166 --> 02:10:57,540
还要六根炸药
And six sticks of dynamite.

1487
02:10:57,541 --> 02:10:58,541
六根?
Six?

1488
02:10:59,541 --> 02:11:00,791
你要猎捕什么?
What are you hunting?

1489
02:11:02,375 --> 02:11:03,625
巨兽
Big game.

1490
02:12:11,541 --> 02:12:13,583
不要!
No! No! No!

1491
02:12:22,333 --> 02:12:24,040
维多
Victor.

1492
02:12:24,041 --> 02:12:27,458
只有伤害你时,你才会听我说话
You only listen when I hurt you.

1493
02:12:41,416 --> 02:12:44,957
你对这玩意儿有信心
This. You put your faith in this.

1494
02:12:44,958 --> 02:12:47,375
你认为这会消灭我
You think this will unmake me.

1495
02:12:51,833 --> 02:12:54,790
那就希望点燃后一举成功,不然的话
Hmm.
Light it then and hope it does, but if it does not,

1496
02:12:54,791 --> 02:12:57,749
我会再去找你
I will come for you again.

1497
02:12:57,750 --> 02:12:59,500
点啊!
Light it!

1498
02:13:06,833 --> 02:13:10,208
现在...快逃吧
Now... run.

1499
02:13:47,083 --> 02:13:53,125
你躺在那里,伤痕累累,弃如敝屣
So, there you were, broken and discarded.

1500
02:13:53,875 --> 02:13:55,250
而我
And I,

1501
02:13:56,500 --> 02:13:58,541
又复活了
alive again.

1502
02:14:03,125 --> 02:14:08,166
我能感觉到焦肉在重新生长
I could feel my singed flesh regrowing.

1503
02:14:09,041 --> 02:14:12,916
一身骨头劈啪作响地调整
The crackling of my bones resetting.

1504
02:14:14,041 --> 02:14:20,375
血液从不停跳动的心脏中汨汨流出
The murmur of my blood pumping through my incessant heart.

1505
02:14:21,500 --> 02:14:24,458
死神再次无情离去
And once more finding no mercy,

1506
02:14:25,958 --> 02:14:28,416
我只剩一条路可走
I had but one path.

1507
02:14:40,458 --> 02:14:42,208
于是我们来到了这里
And here we are.

1508
02:14:44,750 --> 02:14:46,666
耗尽一切,无以为继
Spent and done.

1509
02:14:49,541 --> 02:14:53,207
我们都心力交瘁了
No more in us to give or take.

1510
02:14:53,208 --> 02:14:54,999
帐篷外面的血迹...
The blood outside the tent...

1511
02:14:55,000 --> 02:14:56,125
那是我的
It is mine.

1512
02:14:57,458 --> 02:14:58,916
都是我的
All mine.

1513
02:15:00,041 --> 02:15:01,333
我会流血
I will bleed.

1514
02:15:02,875 --> 02:15:04,166
疼痛
Ache.

1515
02:15:04,916 --> 02:15:06,041
受苦
Suffer.

1516
02:15:09,166 --> 02:15:12,000
永无止境
You see, it will never end.

1517
02:15:32,041 --> 02:15:33,583
对不起
I am sorry.

1518
02:15:40,083 --> 02:15:42,125
我悔不当初
Regret consumes me.

1519
02:15:44,166 --> 02:15:46,791
我现在才认清我的人生
And I now regard my life for what it was.

1520
02:15:49,291 --> 02:15:51,708
你将撒手而去,创造者
You will go now, creator.

1521
02:15:54,375 --> 02:15:55,958
悄然消逝
Fade away.

1522
02:15:58,750 --> 02:16:01,416
一下子就结束了
It will all be but a brief moment.

1523
02:16:03,083 --> 02:16:06,041
我的出生、伤悲
My birth. My grief.

1524
02:16:07,041 --> 02:16:08,500
你的失落
Your loss.

1525
02:16:11,000 --> 02:16:13,250
我不会受到惩罚
I will not be punished.

1526
02:16:14,750 --> 02:16:16,500
也不会被赦免
Nor absolved.

1527
02:16:20,833 --> 02:16:22,166
我曾抱持的希望
What hope I had,

1528
02:16:23,250 --> 02:16:24,791
愤怒...
what rage...

1529
02:16:26,666 --> 02:16:28,041
都微不足道了
It is all nothing.

1530
02:16:31,250 --> 02:16:35,708
当初带我来的浪潮,如今要将你带走
The tide that brought me here now comes to take you away.

1531
02:16:38,250 --> 02:16:39,541
我仍得不到解脱
Leaving me stranded.

1532
02:16:47,916 --> 02:16:49,583
原谅我
Forgive me.

1533
02:16:51,375 --> 02:16:52,625
儿子
My son.

1534
02:17:00,708 --> 02:17:05,375
可以的话,就原谅自己,好好活着
And if you have it in your heart, forgive yourself into existence.

1535
02:17:06,125 --> 02:17:08,624
若死神不肯成全你
If death is not to be, then consider this, my son.

1536
02:17:08,625 --> 02:17:10,500
那也别无他法,儿子

1537
02:17:11,083 --> 02:17:12,541
因为你终究会活下去
While you are alive,

1538
02:17:13,791 --> 02:17:16,583
除了活着,你有其他选择吗?
what recourse do you have but to live?

1539
02:17:24,000 --> 02:17:25,083
活下去
Live.

1540
02:17:26,750 --> 02:17:28,000
叫我的名字
Say my name.

1541
02:17:29,833 --> 02:17:32,083
我父亲给了我那个名字
My father gave me that name,

1542
02:17:33,250 --> 02:17:34,541
但那名字毫无意义
and it meant nothing.

1543
02:17:37,083 --> 02:17:39,375
现在我要你再叫我...
Now I ask you to give it back to me...

1544
02:17:41,750 --> 02:17:43,125
最后一次
one last time.

1545
02:17:45,041 --> 02:17:47,291
用你最初的方式叫吧
The way you said it at the beginning.

1546
02:17:48,416 --> 02:17:50,708
当时,那是你的一切
When it meant the world to you.

1547
02:17:56,291 --> 02:17:57,541
维多
Victor.

1548
02:18:00,625 --> 02:18:02,125
我原谅你
I forgive you.

1549
02:18:25,208 --> 02:18:27,875
安息吧,父亲
Rest now, Father.

1550
02:18:32,250 --> 02:18:33,625
或许此刻
Perhaps now,

1551
02:18:35,583 --> 02:18:37,833
我俩能同为人类
we can both be human.

1552
02:18:47,416 --> 02:18:48,250
放下武器
Weapons down.

1553
02:18:49,041 --> 02:18:51,083
- 放下武器 - 我要对我的人负责
- Put the weapons down! - I am responsible for my men.

1554
02:18:52,583 --> 02:18:53,833
他可以离开
He can leave.

1555
02:20:28,708 --> 02:20:29,707
脱困了!
We are free!

1556
02:20:29,708 --> 02:20:31,125
我们自由了!

1557
02:20:32,708 --> 02:20:33,833
船长...
Captain...

1558
02:20:34,833 --> 02:20:36,207
你要下什么命令?
What are your orders?

1559
02:20:36,208 --> 02:20:37,749
调整航向
Man the sails.

1560
02:20:37,750 --> 02:20:38,832
掉头回去
Turn around.

1561
02:20:38,833 --> 02:20:40,665
你要告诉大家吗?
Do you want to tell the men?

1562
02:20:40,666 --> 02:20:41,708
大伙们!
Men!

1563
02:20:42,916 --> 02:20:44,166
我们返航!
We're sailing home!

1564
02:20:44,750 --> 02:20:45,833
回家吧!
We're sailing home!

1565
02:21:38,333 --> 02:21:43,583
(「纵然会心碎,仍得苟延于世」 - 拜伦勋爵)

